rows.label: qst105704_msg0001
rows.name:
Pray tell, Zadazan...
What cause such ruckus?

rows.label: qst105704_msg0003
rows.name:
Don has heard of you.
Don know who you are!

rows.label: qst105704_msg0004
rows.name:
You stand before the mighty...
Don!

rows.label: qst105704_msg0005
rows.name:
Yes, Dondon is Don of Lindwurm!
Secret organization pulling strings
of Avaritia Guild!

rows.label: qst105704_msg0006
rows.name:
Mah-hah-hah-meh!
Your bewilderment pleases Don!
Lindwurm very secret organization!

rows.label: qst105704_msg0007
rows.name:
Was never desire of Don to interfere
directly in overworld matters...

rows.label: qst105704_msg0008
rows.name:
But now Bahn, sonnypon of Don,
is captive of Empire...
That change many things.

rows.label: qst105704_msg0009
rows.name:
Fury of Don know no limit.
After Superbia, will crush Invidia!
Then Gula!

rows.label: qst105704_msg0010
rows.name:
And truth be told, final part of
plan was to crush you.

rows.label: qst105704_msg0011
rows.name:
But plan can change!
Come to surface now with Don,
and witness glory of Lindwurm!
